The network consists of over 447,808 miles of equivalent road mileage. The data set covers the 48 contiguous States plus the District of Columbia, Alaska, and Hawaii. The nominal scale of the data set is 1:100,000 with a maximal positional error of \ufffd\ufffd\ufffd\ufffd80 meters.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>transportation</dcat:keyword>
